<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Yashvardhan - Professional Portfolio</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
            -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; /* Mobile touch highlight remove karne ke liye */
        }

        body {
            background-color: #0f172a;
            color: #f8fafc;
        }

        span {
            color: #38bdf8;
        }

        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px 5%;
            background-color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid #1e293b;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        nav a {
            color: #94a3b8;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
        }

        nav a:active {
            color: #38bdf8;
        }

        .btn-nav {
            background: #38bdf8;
            color: #0f172a !important;
            padding: 6px 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: transform 0.1s ease;
        }

        .btn-nav:active {
            transform: scale(0.95);
        }

        .hero {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0 20px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #1e293b 0%, #0f172a 70%);
        }

        .hero-content h1 {
            font-size: 40px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.3;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .hero-content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #94a3b8;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto 30px auto;
        }

        .hero-buttons a {
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: transform 0.1s ease, opacity 0.2s;
        }

        /* Touch Effects for Buttons */
        .hero-buttons a:active {
            transform: scale(0.95);
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #38bdf8;
            color: #0f172a;
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            border: 2px solid #38bdf8;
            color: #38bdf8;
        }

        .services {
            padding: 80px 5%;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #0b0f19;
        }

        .services h2 {
            font-size: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .services-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        /* Touch Effect for Cards */
        .service-card {
            background-color: #1e293b;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #334155;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s;
        }

        .service-card:active {
            transform: scale(0.98);
            border-color: #38bdf8;
            background-color: #1e293b;
        }

        .service-card h3 {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .service-card p {
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        footer {
            padding: 60px 5% 20px 5%;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #0f172a;
            border-top: 1px solid #1e293b;
        }

        footer h2 {
            font-size: 26px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        footer p {
            color: #94a3b8;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .contact-info {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #f8fafc;
            line-height: 2;
        }

        .contact-info a {
            color: #38bdf8;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: transform 0.1s ease;
        }

        .contact-info a:active {
            transform: scale(0.95);
        }

        .footer-bottom {
            margin-top: 40px;
            border-top: 1px solid #1e293b;
            padding-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #64748b;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            nav {
                display: none;
            }
            .hero-content h1 {
                font-size: 32px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="logo">Yash<span>vardhan</span></div>
        <nav>
            <a href="#home">Home</a>
            <a href="#about">Education</a>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn-nav">Contact</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section id="home" class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Welcome To My <br><span>Professional Portfolio</span></h1>
            <p>Hi, I am Yashvardhan. I build clean, fast, and modern digital experiences. Explore my profile and get in touch for collaborations.</p>
            <div class="hero-buttons">
                <a href="#about" class="btn-primary">My Education</a>
                <a href="#contact" class="btn-secondary">Contact Me</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="services">
        <h2>Education & Expertise</h2>
        <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="service-card">
                <h3>Basic Computer Diploma</h3>
                <p>Gained fundamental knowledge of computer operations, software handling, and digital workflows.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card">
                <h3>Web Technology</h3>
                <p>Learning and implementing modern front-end web designs with standard responsive codes.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card">
                <h3>Digital Solutions</h3>
                <p>Providing clean layout designs optimized for mobile phones and modern browsers.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer id="contact">
        <h2>Let's Connect</h2>
        <p>Feel free to reach out to me for any projects or inquiries.</p>
        
        <div class="contact-info">
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:ryashvardhan58@gmail.com">ryashvardhan58@gmail.com</a></p>
            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:8492887585">+91 8492887585</a></p>
        </div>

        <a href="mailto:ryashvardhan58@gmail.com" class="btn-primary" style="text-decoration: none;">Send Email Directly</a>
        
        <div class="footer-bottom">
            <p>&copy; 2026 Yashvardhan. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>

